{"tid":2517631,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"日企停用中國製無人機","createTime":"2021-05-05T12:15:09.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-05T12:29:26.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7dd1908d8f85d34c69caef50f46402c7195f0e2d","tid":2517631,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T12:15:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20210505/NIDYCZYXEBCEHC75HXYQCJWJFA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20210505%2FNIDYCZYXEBCEHC75HXYQCJWJFA%2F&d=d89kjzbMxLru5B8Znw6mn%2BIs%2Fr43DZ9KHrtYDEqBsnw%3D&h=61d14d62\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20210505%2FNIDYCZYXEBCEHC75HXYQCJWJFA%2F&h=c0f8a6c3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20210505/NIDYCZYXEBCEHC75HXYQCJWJFA/</a><br />\n<br />\n日企停用中國製無人機<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/eNLlXviolkNzcRmQ7KZ97EDI53M=/510x341/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/EOQNO5ZZX5GHTOK5LX6JMKHYPI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FeNLlXviolkNzcRmQ7KZ97EDI53M%3D%2F510x341%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FEOQNO5ZZX5GHTOK5LX6JMKHYPI.jpg&h=e589079a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■日本電信電話株式會社計劃停用中國生產的無人機。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n據《日本經濟新聞》周二引述消息稱，日本電訊巨擘日本電信電話株式會社（NTT）及九州電力等日本企業，為免受到潛在數據安全風險的威脅，已計劃停用中國生產的無人機，尋求用日本生產的無人機作為替代。報道稱日本NTT及其子公司主要使用中國出產的大疆創新無人機，還有日本和瑞士出產的無人機來檢查橋樑上的電纜。九州電力公司亦考慮以日本製造的產品，頂替由大疆創新的無人機。"},{"pid":"aac442a07cd8f261b0b9cd6dbd9e4d6624e6bc02","tid":2517631,"uid":284855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T12:16:55.000Z","msg":"一早應該, 宜家仲用無人機廵電纜, 一個唔該畀人有意後門控制炒埋落電纜度就分分鐘成個城無電<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7a82ecdbdca3f37eb0c52eeaf15dd996875655f","tid":2517631,"uid":191926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T12:18:42.000Z","msg":"諗起eh<br />\n<br />\n上年曾經既 youtuber愛股<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d79dd09874dd5493aacb5905ee51d1a09c25682","tid":2517631,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T12:29:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}